import React from 'react'
import { Card, CardCategory, FlexWrapper, StyledCard } from './Styled'
import { Swiper, SwiperSlide } from "swiper/react";
import "swiper/css";
import "swiper/css/pagination";
import { Pagination } from "swiper";


function Cards() {
  return (
      <Swiper
      >
        <SwiperSlide>
          <StyledCard>
            <CardCategory>POP</CardCategory>
          </StyledCard>
        </SwiperSlide>
        <SwiperSlide>
          <Card>
            <CardCategory>INDIE</CardCategory>
          </Card>
        </SwiperSlide>
        <SwiperSlide>
          <StyledCard>
            <CardCategory>RAP</CardCategory>
          </StyledCard>
        </SwiperSlide>
        <SwiperSlide>
          <Card>
            <CardCategory>RETRO</CardCategory>
          </Card>
        </SwiperSlide>
      </Swiper>
  );
}

export default Cards
